      "bookmarkId": "43685146_6_2543-2573",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2543-2573",
      "markText": "当你无法更加努力时，就该寻找一条更简单的路了。",
      "totalCount": 1200,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43685146&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2543&rangeEnd=2573",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/56132d80729a951a561ae48?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2543&rangeEnd=2573"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43685146_9_1668-1738",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "1668-1738",
      "markText": "我们的大脑天生会优先考虑那些“情感价值”高的情绪，如恐惧、怨恨或愤怒，这些强烈的情绪通常会胜出，因此，留给我们解决重要问题的脑力资源就更少了",
      "totalCount": 1088,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43685146&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1668&rangeEnd=1738",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/56132d80729a951a561ae48?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1668&rangeEnd=1738"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43685146_4_807-850",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "807-850",
      "markText": "“当你专注于你所缺乏的，你会失去你所拥有的；当你专注于你所拥有的，你会得到你所缺乏的”",
      "totalCount": 1064,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43685146&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=807&rangeEnd=850",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/56132d80729a951a561ae48?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=807&rangeEnd=850"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43685146_3_2307-2324",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2307-2324",
      "markText": "不只要做正确的事，更要正确地做事。",
      "totalCount": 900,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43685146&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2307&rangeEnd=2324",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/56132d80729a951a561ae48?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2307&rangeEnd=2324"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43685146_10_1815-1896",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "1815-1896",
      "markText": "问题就在于，现代生活的复杂性使人们用一种错误的二分法把事情粗暴地分为“重要且艰难的”和“容易且琐碎的”。大多数人奉它为铁律：容易的事情都不重要，艰难的事情才重要。",
